Hi Blazej,

Thanks for raising this issue.
We have fixed the vulnerability and have released a hot fix release today. We will send out a security advisory to all our customers shortly.


You can upgrade PMP to latest version or install the new version 8101 to fix the issue. You can access the release notes from the below mentioned link.


https://www.manageengine.com/products/passwordmanagerpro/release-notes.html


Let us know if you have any further questions.

Thanks & Regards,Mike
[Technical Consultant | Password Manager Pro]






